Maralal town chief Selina Lemakara fears for her life after CID police officers from Maralal police station allegedly broke into her home, destroyed property and assaulted her on Saturday evening.She said three CID officers went away with iron sheets, fencing posts and Sh30,000. They came here when I was away, broke the gate and got access to my home, Lemakara said.She found them loading goods into a police vehicle. When she questioned them, one officer beat her up, Lemakara said.